#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"NV Speech Player is a free and open-source prototype speech synthesizer that "
"can be used by NVDA. It generates speech using Klatt synthesis, making it "
"somewhat similar to speech synthesizers such as Dectalk and Eloquence."
msgstr ""
"NV Speech Player je eksperimentalan sintetizator otvorenog koda i može se "
"besplatno koristiti uz NVDA. Generira govor koristeći Klatt sintezu, što ga "
"čini sličnim sintetizatorima kao što su Dectalk i Eloquence."

